text:
Chiyoko's headband,
it kinda moves with her as she moves.
It sways quite a bit, doesn't it?

Oh, hey! Why are you laughing?!
Was it because of the "myon myon" thing?!

Myon...!
Haha, just stop with the "myon" for now...!

If it's "byon byon"... it feels too springy,
so maybe something like "byuuun"...!?

Wha- Producer-san, don't get too amused!
And could you please tell me the correct answer!
